# Strudel-Open-Songs
Open-Source Songs for Strudel.cc

Nuthin' but a "G" Thang - Dr. Dre (1992) :



/*
@title:chronic
@by:dre
song @by dr.dre
*/
setcpm(203/4)
samples('github:dissonancefm/samples')
$: s("sample16")
  .loopAt(4).adsr(".0:.0:1:.0")
  .soft(".3:.9")
$: s("sample15")
  .loopAt(4).adsr(".0:.0:1:.0")
  .soft(".3:1").lpf(5234)
$: s("b12").loopAt(4).gain(.52)
$: s("b4").loopAt(4).gain(.6)
$: s("bd:6!4").degradeBy(.5).rib(1,234).soft(".6:2.9")
